fallback movies completely.</span><br><span>Delete:</span></p><ul data-spread="false"><li><p><span>Inception</span></p></li><li><p><span>Pathaan</span></p></li><li><p><span>Squid Game</span></p></li></ul><p><span>The application must load movies only from movies.json.</span></p><p><span>BUG 2:</span><br><span>Edit Movie is not working correctly.</span></p><p><span>After entering the correct password:</span></p><ul data-spread="false"><li><p><span>Open the Add/Edit form automatically.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Load all selected movie data into the form.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Allow editing of:</span></p><ul data-spread="false"><li><p><span>Title</span></p></li><li><p><span>Year</span></p></li><li><p><span>Origin</span></p></li><li><p><span>Type</span></p></li><li><p><span>IMDb</span></p></li><li><p><span>Poster Path</span></p></li></ul></li><li><p><span>Saving must update the movie immediately.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Updated movie must appear correctly in the list.</span></p></li></ul><p><span>BUG 3:</span><br><span>Delete Movie is inconsistent.</span></p><p><span>After entering the correct password and confirming:</span></p><ul data-spread="false"><li><p><span>Remove the movie immediately.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Refresh statistics.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Refresh filters.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Refresh search results.</span></p></li><li><p><span>Do not allow deleted movies to reappear unless they still exist in movies.json.</span></p></li></ul><p><span>PASSWORD RULES</span></p><p><span>Password:</span><br><span>Afridi10@</span></p><ul data-spread="false"><li><p><span>Add Movie = No password</span></p></li><li><p><span>Edit Movie = Password Required</span></p></li><li><p><span>Delete Movie = Password Required</span></p></li></ul><p><span>YEAR SORTING</span></p><p><span>Movies must always be displayed year-wise in descending order.</span></p><p><span>Example:</span></p><p><span>2026</span><br><span>2025</span><br><span>2024</span><br><span>2023</span><br><span>2022</span></p><p><span>Newest year first.</span></p><p><span>Within each year section, sort movie titles alphabetically.</span></p><p><span>Example:</span></p><p><span>2024</span><br><span>A Movie</span><br><span>B Movie</span><br><span>C Movie</span></p><p><span>Statistics, filters, and search must continue working correctly.</span></p><p><span>SUCCESS MESSAGE</span></p><p><span>After Edit or Delete show:</span></p><p><span>"Remember to export/download the updated data before uploading to GitHub."</span></p><p><span>IMPORTANT</span></p><p><span>Do not redesign the UI.</span><br><span>Do not change colors.</span><br><span>Do not change theme.</span><br><span>Do not remove existing features.</span></p><p><span>Only:</span></p><ul data-spread="false"><li><p><span>Fix Edit</span></p></li><li><p><span>Fix Delete</span></p></li><li><p><span>Remove demo movies</span></p></li><li><p><span>Enforce year-wise descending sorting</span></p></li><li><p><span>Keep all existing functionality</span></p></li></ul><p><span>Return the complete corrected code.</span></p></div></div></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-2 rounded-[24px] shadow-[inset_0px_0px_0px_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07)]" data-writing-block-fullscreen-shell-border="true"></div></div></div>
