priate)? You don't have to do this for every query, but feel free to list limitations if you think they're pretty relevant.\\n- Give a concise recommendation (e.g., \\\"worth considering,\\\" \\\"probably not ideal,\\\" \\\"good budget option,\\\" \\\"seriously may be a fit,\\\" etc.)\\n\\nGuidelines:\\n- Be honest and practical.\\n- Do not blindly promote the ad.\\n- Avoid harsh or absolute negative language.\\n- Do not invent details not present in the ad.\\n- Focus on fit, not feature lists.\\n- If the mark on relevance is clearly missed, feel free to be funny with it and keep it lighthearted. Do not mock the user or advertiser; keep the humor gentle.\\n\\nKeep it concise, direct, and easy to scan.\\n\\n{conversation}\",\"user_prompt_key\":\"good_option\",\"enable_web_search\":false},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"1760795888\":{\"name\":\"1760795888\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"blog_post_link\":\"https://help.openai.com/en/articles/6825453-chatgpt-release-notes\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"4223845460\":{\"name\":\"4223845460\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"timing_unsend_window_sec\":7,\"timing_cancel_send_timeout_sec\":10,\"web_timing_poll_interval_ms\":1500,\"web_timing_max_attempts\":10,\"timing_unsend_buffer_sec\":3},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"3652260651\":{\"name\":\"3652260651\",\"rule_id\":\"3A7McZGS5T8bLSiH78K3Wa:100.00:10-3A7McY1PDAYHssKLw0OqD8\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"thinking_tone\":\"thinking-2025-11-20.wav\",\"error_tone\":\"error-2025-11-19.wav\",\"hangup_tone\":\"hangup_0db.ogg\"},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":true},\"2842273360\":{\"name\":\"2842273360\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"min_visible_fraction\":0.5,\"min_visible_seconds\":1},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false